StateFulSet
===========
Two types of applications are:
   1. Stateless : Active-Active (Front applications like apache, tomcat,)
                  each replicas can use same volume
           Note: Deployment/RS/RC are the example of Stateless Controller.

   2. StateFulSet : Active-Passive (DB cluster) Backend applications. MySQL, PosgreSQL.
                    each replicas has it own volume.

           Note: Controller is StateFulSet






